summary: While researching for how to take care of the pokemon egg I was entrusted with, I have learnt that the shells on a Togepi's body...
body: While researching for how to take care of the pokemon egg I was entrusted with, I have learnt that the shells on a Togepi’s body is not actually a part of it’s body and can be removed, however this is not recommended, since it can store positive energies inside of it and thus will become very unhappy without it.
